A linked address database

Take2 - Address-Datenbank

*** New Features

* stelle emails grafisch dar to avoid spam
* internationalization http://blog.yjl.im/2009/02/using-django-i18n-in-google-app-engine.html
* User Avatars
* Weblinks blenden das Icon der Seite ein
* Gmail oeffnen wenn auf email adresse geklickt wird
* PDF Adress-Liste export
* take photos with webcam
* vcard import (or ideally, by forwarding vcard emails to weschnitz)
* ldap interface for mail addresses
* special layout for smartphones
* Unsubscribe
* Export data for christmas card lists or other meetups

*** Development process

* Upload
./appcfg.py --no_cookies -e stefan@weschnitz.com update ../take2

* manage application:
https://appengine.google.com/

*** History

I have two appspots
- take2wesch for the application using a high replication datastore and
- take2nitz which uses master/slave


